description	"Mitth'raw'nuruodo

Class: Bounty Hunter.
Class Summary: 
An agile pistoleer commander and medic with Force Block (Ysalimari)

Weaponry:
- Pistol (3)
- Frag Grenades (2)
- Sonic Detonator (2)
- Fire Grenade (1)

Attributes:
- Rally
- Can view ally stats

Force Abilities:
- Jump (1)
- Ysalimari (Force Block 2)
- Advanced Deductive Abilities (Sense 3)
- Force Regen 70% slower

Inventory:
- Binoculars
- Bacta (25+ HP)
- Big Bacta (50+ HP)
- Seeker Drone

Abilities:
- Can recover allies' health and armor (Press the 'Use' key while adjacent and facing teammate with low health)
- Can view ally stats
- Dodge (2) [Class Special 1]
- Flipkick (2)

Mitth'raw'nuruodo, better known as 'Thrawn', was well known as a brilliant and ruthless strategist. He believed that in order to achieve victory in war, one must know their enemy. As such, he dedicated himself to understanding the philosophy, art, and culture of his opponents."